*pidgin-facebookchat-1.51 (13 Jun 2009)

  13 Jun 2009; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  +pidgin-facebookchat-1.51.ebuild:
  Version bump, adds gzip compression, display messages sent from website,
  inbox count, bold and underline formatting, fixes idle status,
  notifications for non-English users, usernames with utf-8 characters,
  buddies appearing offline when they weren't, some crashes on disconnect,
  and uses new channel finding code

